text: Henri king gret ealle his biscopes & eorles & his scirgereuan & þeinas & his wicneras Frencisce & Englisce ouer eall Englaland freondlice.

Ic <kywe> eow ðæt ic habbe <geumen> gode & Sancte Petre & þan biscope on Winceastre Willelme & his munecan þæne ylcan freodom & þa gerihta þe þæt mynster hæfde on Eadwardes kynges dæge & on mines fæder & on mines broþer dæge on lande & on strande, on wydan & on feldan & on læsan & sace & socne binnan port & butan, toll & team & infangeneþeof, forsteall, <giþbrece>, <hansocne> & mundbrice & ælc wite læsse & mare swa frig swa hi frigost hæfdon on ænies kinges oððe biscopes dæge þe ætforan us wæron.

And ic forbeode þæt nan mann ne beo swa dyrstig þæt heom fram handan drage heononford ænig þæra þinga þæs þe hi rihtlice agon & into þan minstre gebyrige oððe on landon oððe on mannon oððe on ænigon oþron æhton.
And gif hit swa do wite he þæt hyt binnon þrym nihton ongean cume be eallon þam þe manage.
